sql:
SELECT people_with_disabilities
FROM age_group_disability_data
WHERE year = 2023 AND age_group_id = 1;

external_knowledge:
- Diabetes and Hypertension are health conditions with unique condition IDs (0 and 1 respectively) in the health_conditions table; 
- The prevalence rate is calculated as the proportion of people with the condition among those with disabilities; 
- The year 2023 is the specified year for which the disability statistics are retrieved.
